{"tid":1319430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢見到趕狗唔一定需要好多人","createTime":"2019-07-15T07:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T11:07:18.000Z","uid":139931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa5cb3b5516b5800c54de6c2ae508916471f90c","tid":1319430,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:06:36.000Z","msg":"反而有膽 夠惡最緊要<br />\n發夢見到有白狗+3-4個低裝藍狗係比較少人既商場門口出黎挑釁<br />\n我地作勢想開佢波佢地就縮<br />\n見佢地縮我地就食住上追鳩住班狗入埋商場追多兩步撤退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我地上前既只有十零個左右 係有幾個比較高大<br />\n<br />\n睇返上水橋底咁多人圍住班便衣狗都比個肥婆任噴真係差天共地<br />\n<br />\nbtw趕狗果陣有人不停叫唔好 難聽過粗口 你叫唔好即係比狗知有人會限制住我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋對峙時唔該女人真係唔好企前面 排骨 雞仔聲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f316313b1820e9852717f18251d5274a8b96b76f","tid":1319430,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"感謝一齊上既隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e83a7e7cb0cd45200674df5df51cef14e4d759","tid":1319430,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1b248b133cf11201264ac0d7ad6fff831bd20aa0","tid":1319430,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}